title.narrative: WATCH NL

description.narrative: WATCH NL combats the sexual exploitation of children in the Netherlands by conducting (online) investigation into the potential perpetrators. Information on those human traffickers will be send to Law Enforcement Agencies or the abusers will be warned by ourselves digitally.  A hotline is in place, with our partner CoMensha, to receive reports on potential situations of sexual exploitation. These reports will be triaged and reffered to the relevant organisations, investigated by the CyberUnit of Terre des Hommes and information will be analysed to get a clear view on the trends.
Expenditure 2020
